-- U.K. Pound Erases 0.3 Percent Decline Against Dollar to Trade at $1.5394
-- Paul Dobson
-- 2010-09-07T07:12:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-07/u-k-pound-erases-0-3-percent-decline-against-dollar-to-trade-at-1-5394.html

          
          
             The pound erased its decline against
the dollar to trade little changed at $1.5394 at 8:10 a.m. in
London. Sterling earlier dropped as much as 0.3 percent to
$1.5353.  
 The U.K. currency extended gains versus the euro,
appreciating 0.6 percent to 83.13 pence.  
